snippet.title: reflex runner - 2d platformer
snippet.description: reflex runner is a speed running platformer that increases in difficulty as you progress through more than 25 unique levels. the goal is to clear each level as fast as possible dodging razor sharp saw blades, red hot lasers, shooting flames and much more! the idea behind the game was to create a community of speed runners competing against one another for world record clear times and bragging rights.
